We've met with this in some similar situations.
Unfortunately, in the text of the recently adopted Telecommunications Act, the <0xC4><0x8C>T<0xC3><0x9A>’s extension of its competence in the field of economic competition in telecommunications has not been able to be overcome, although this has led to many experts hoping to improve the situation.
Representatives of the <0xC3><0x9A>OHS should know this well, but they probably have other interests.
It works when no one is watching.
In the meantime, the operation of some kind of al-virtual service providers remains unnoticed, many of which already operate in the Czech mobile networks.
