At the same time, none of the service providers are protected against such a procedure.
In fact, these companies have a negligible profit from their activities, and in the meantime, unlike real virtual service providers, they are not particularly threatened by their own official marketing.
Miroslav <0xC4><0x8C>epick<0xC3><0xBD> warns of possible problems: “The law allows similar speculation, but only a negligible percentage of customers use the services of these companies.
